Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.09,0:27:20.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.05,0:27:25.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}如果给美国人喘息之机  他们会占上风
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.10,0:27:35.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}因此我们必须通过摧毁他们的航母  对他们进行毁灭性的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.27,0:27:37.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜您  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Congratulations, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.79,0:27:39.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,您是领导海军的正确人选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're the right man to run the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.45,0:27:42.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们一遇到麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When they get in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.41,0:27:44.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,就会派出不好惹的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they send for the sons of bitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.93,0:27:52.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的首要任务必须是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our priority must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.37,0:27:56.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}夺取我们所需的资源
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.84,0:28:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}这是陆军的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.76,0:28:05.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}而海军的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.60,0:28:10.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}就是带我们过去  再带我们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.56,0:28:17.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,太平洋上的形势\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The situation in the Pacific is far worse
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.12,0:28:18.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,远比所报告的糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than has been reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.63,0:28:20.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有三艘航母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have three carriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.02,0:28:21.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,日军有十艘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Japs have ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.85,0:28:24.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一艘能用的战列舰都没有  而他们有九艘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have zero functional battleships, they have nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.47,0:28:29.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们有更多的巡洋舰  轰炸机  战斗机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They have more cruisers, more bombers, more fighters, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.69,0:28:31.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们的很多装备都更先进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}much of their equipment is more modern.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.65,0:28:34.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们只能指望现有的兵力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll just have to count on the men that we have out there
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.82,0:28:37.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以抵挡得住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to hold the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.26,0:28:40.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,新任司令的工作可真不好做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't envy the new commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.84,0:28:49.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.38,0:28:54.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,总统亲自指定了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The president asked for you himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.86,0:29:03.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说你应该前往珍珠港  留在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He said that you should get the hell out to Pearl and stay there
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.73,0:29:07.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,直到我们的舰队驶入东京湾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until our ships sail into Tokyo Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.25,0:29:17.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎接手这个世上最艰难的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Welcome to the most difficult job in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.01,0:29:24.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}陆军把我们卷入了这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.63,0:29:27.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}现在却希望我们载着他们到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.76,0:29:31.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}暂时而已  情况会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.06,0:29:36.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(192,235)}我希望你开始起草我们讨论过的行动计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want you to start drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.81,0:29:41.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad1\\c&HDBDAD7&\pos(188,235)}中途岛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.03,0:29:51.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,全体注意  立正\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Detail. A-ten-hut!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.98,0:29:56.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,预备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.75,0:29:57.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.86,0:29:58.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.83,0:30:00.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.53,0:30:02.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.86,0:30:04.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.09,0:30:06.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.07,0:30:12.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,节哀顺变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.70,0:30:15.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊想成为像你一样的飞行员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Roy wanted to be a pilot like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.95,0:30:18.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我劝他放弃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I talked him out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.76,0:30:20.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说太危险了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said it was too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.10,0:30:25.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,下场葬礼上再见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll see you at the next funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.74,0:30:27.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不必出席的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.07,0:30:28.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.46,0:30:30.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们是一家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.16,0:30:37.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just wanna say...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.39,0:30:39.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊·皮尔斯是我认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Roy Pearce was one of the finest bastards
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.98,0:30:41.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,最好的混蛋之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.34,0:30:43.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以谈他谈上一个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I could talk about the man for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.50,0:30:45.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我应该把这任务留给你们这些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I think that's a job I'll leave up to one of you boys
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.24,0:30:46.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,和他一起进了军官学校的小伙们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that went to the Academy with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.21,0:30:49.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.13,0:30:53.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  我可不能让某个开鱼雷机的为罗伊致辞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, well, I can't let some torpedo jockey speak for Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.61,0:30:56.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是没优秀到能从企业号上起飞的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Especially one not good enough to fly from Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.74,0:30:59.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.88,0:31:06.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,刚进军官学校那年的夏天  我  罗伊还有迪基\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Summer after plebe year, me, Roy and Dickie
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.33,0:31:09.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,去探望了住在五大湖区的罗伊的叔叔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}went up to visit Roy's uncle, up in the Great Lakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.63,0:31:10.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,当年的禁酒令最为严厉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was the peak of Prohibition,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.74,0:31:12.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以有天晚上  我们决定航行到加拿大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so one night, we decide to sail to Canada
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.58,0:31:14.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,买一桶啤酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to buy a keg of beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.46,0:31:16.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我们回去的路上  太阳马上就要升起时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On our way back, right before the sun comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.45,0:31:18.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,风停了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the wind dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.47,0:31:20.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们就\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, there we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.03,0:31:23.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,漂浮在了湖中央\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just floating in the middle of the lake,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.12,0:31:25.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,等着边境巡逻队出现救我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}waiting for the Border Patrol to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.51,0:31:28.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说我们应该把酒丢掉  但罗伊...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said we should just ditch the booze, but Roy...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.90,0:31:30.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,迪基\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, Dickie,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.13,0:31:31.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what did Roy say?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.29,0:31:32.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,"想都别想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Hell, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.54,0:31:34.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要喝光"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll drink it all."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.65,0:31:41.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊曾是我的伴郎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Roy was my best man.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.51,0:31:46.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是我女儿的教父\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was the godfather to my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.81,0:31:49.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我原以为将来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.57,0:31:52.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们会一起坐在门廊上  喝着啤酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we'd be on a porch, drinking beers,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.08,0:31:54.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,对我们在大战中的表现大肆吹嘘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}telling lies about what we did in the big war.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.36,0:32:03.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,敬罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.77,0:32:04.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,敬罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.22,0:32:06.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,敬罗伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.19,0:32:10.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Man, oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.36,0:32:11.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么让我喝了这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why'd you make me drink so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.24,0:32:14.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可能得送我回家了  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You might have to carry me home, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.17,0:32:17.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,该死  海岸巡逻队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, shit. Shore Patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.32,0:32:20.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  那是上将的旗帜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, that's the admiral's flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.67,0:32:22.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是新任司令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, I bet it's the new commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.49,0:32:23.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.95,0:32:25.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,看着像尼米兹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That looks like Nimitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.29,0:32:26.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,听说他是个忠将\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hear he's true-blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.02,0:32:28.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,尼米兹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, Nimitz!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.35,0:32:30.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候才派我们去打小日本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When are you going to let us at those Japs?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.19,0:32:32.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.39,0:32:33.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,要我去记下他们的名字吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you want me to get their names?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.64,0:32:35.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.60,0:32:36.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,他好像听到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think he might have heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.26,0:32:41.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴至少还有小伙子斗志满满\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm glad at least some of the boys still want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.15,0:32:57.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到珍珠港  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Welcome to Pearl, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.53,0:32:59.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是莱顿少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm Lieutenant Commander Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.50,0:33:01.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.94,0:33:03.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,那您应该会理解我的请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, then you'll understand my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.86,0:33:06.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想被调到一艘驱逐舰上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish to be reassigned to a destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.02,0:33:09.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是试图警告过前任司令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Didn't you try to warn my predecessor
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.00,0:33:10.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,可能有突袭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about the impending attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.78,0:33:11.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,不完全是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.40,0:33:14.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说的是我们跟丢了敌军的航母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said that we had lost track of the enemy carriers
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.91,0:33:16.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,需要做好防备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and needed to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.70,0:33:19.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我应该更强硬点的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I should've pushed harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.59,0:33:22.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想  这个教训\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A lesson, I assume,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.68,0:33:24.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你已经永生难忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you have taken to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.38,0:33:25.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.50,0:33:28.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是要为美国史上最大情报失误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm the intelligence officer responsible for overseeing the greatest
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.91,0:33:31.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,负责的情报官员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}intelligence failure in American history.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.32,0:33:34.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,关上门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.10,0:33:39.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在士气处于最低点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Morale is at an all-time low
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.37,0:33:40.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,但完全可以理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and for good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.84,0:33:44.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,日军正以骇人的速度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Japanese are advancing on all fronts
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.36,0:33:45.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,在各条战线上推进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at a terrifying pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.97,0:33:47.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I, nevertheless,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.31,0:33:50.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还是知道我们的士兵有斗志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}know the fighting spirit of our men.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.13,0:33:53.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我对他们有信心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I have faith in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.35,0:33:56.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我还需要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I also need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.29,0:33:58.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们对自己有信心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that they have faith in themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.69,0:34:01.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你成为我的山本大将\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need you to be my Admiral Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.86,0:34:04.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,以他的角度思考  告诉我他的下一步意图\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get in his head. Tell me what he's going to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.78,0:34:06.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的第一个任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your first assignment...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.88,0:34:08.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是我们需要发起进攻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we need to throw a punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.40,0:34:09.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,不止是为了提振士气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not just for morale,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.57,0:34:13.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,还要让日本人知道挨打是什么感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but so the Japanese know what it feels like to be hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.87,0:34:17.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要派哈尔西去攻击马绍尔群岛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sending Halsey to attack the Marshall Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.29,0:34:18.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我需要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.21,0:34:20.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会遭受埋伏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that they're not walking into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.68,0:34:31.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1\fad(1500,1200)\c&H06126F&\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\pos(364.2,170.4)}1942年2月1日
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.35,0:34:31.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1\fad(1500,1200)\c&H06126F&\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\pos(363.6,221.6)}马绍尔群岛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.97,0:34:32.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,目标是莱岛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The target is Roi Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.74,0:34:35.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的潜艇报告那里存在船只航行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our submarines have reported shipping traffic
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.44,0:34:37.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,并有一个军用机场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and one military airfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.51,0:34:38.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不清楚目标的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't know what we're facing,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.73,0:34:41.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以能打多狠打多狠  然后撤离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so hit 'em as hard as possible and then get the hell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.91,0:34:43.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,那敌军航母呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So what about the enemy carrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.71,0:34:46.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,情报称他们在三千多公里之外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Intelligence says they're 2,000 miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.20,0:34:47.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是说之前那群\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean the same group of geniuses
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.41,0:34:49.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知道小日本要袭击珍珠港的天才吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who didn't know the Japs were gunning for Pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.68,0:34:50.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,如我所说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.80,0:34:52.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,做好万全准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}be prepared for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.88,0:34:59.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,早起的鸟儿有虫吃  先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The early bird catches the worm, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.83,0:35:00.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要趁小日本还没起床\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're gonna hit that anchorage
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.84,0:35:03.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,袭击那片锚泊地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before the Japs have even rolled out of bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.66,0:35:06.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,他的口水都把鞋子洗干净了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looks like he spit polished his shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.91,0:35:09.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们  我们要全身而退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, guys, let's get home in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.13,0:35:10.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.88,0:35:14.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,计划是什么  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the plan, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.05,0:35:16.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,其他中队会先发起攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The other squadrons will strike first.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.26,0:35:19.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们进场  清理掉剩下的目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then we go in and clean up the remaining targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.00,0:35:20.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,小日本那时会对我们有所防备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Japs will know we're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.49,0:35:22.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,要是我们被击落怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happens if we get shot down?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.28,0:35:24.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我不会沦为战俘的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I'm not gonna end up as a POW.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.82,0:35:26.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,你也不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And neither are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.30,0:35:36.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了一个大型目标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got a large target in my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.46,0:35:38.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,飞到足够接近的位置来提高命中率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get close enough to make it count.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.90,0:35:47.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,开始行动  伙计们  发射鱼雷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Start your runs, boys. Engage torpedoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.79,0:36:22.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,看起来进攻莱岛的部队捅了马蜂窝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looks like our boys on Roi poked a hornet's nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.18,0:36:29.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们遇到了一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.27,0:36:32.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在塔罗亚岛发现了第二个敌军机场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got eyes on a second enemy airfield on Taroa Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.32,0:36:35.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,目测大概有三十架轰炸机  并有重型战斗机掩护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm counting maybe 30 bombers and heavy fighter cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.41,0:36:37.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,听到了吗  伙计们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You hear that, boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.79,0:36:39.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不摧毁那个机场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we don't knock out that airfield,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.21,0:36:41.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们会袭击企业号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they'll go after Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.26,0:36:43.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,这次战斗结束后  我还希望有能降落的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I want a place to land when this is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.52,0:37:00.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,敌军战斗机  十一点钟方向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enemy fighters, 11 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.15,0:37:02.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,遭遇敌机  开始行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We got company. Start your runs!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.56,0:37:29.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,九百米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}3,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.09,0:37:38.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,六百一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}2,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.66,0:37:40.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,五百八\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1,900!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.10,0:37:41.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,五百五\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1,800!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.48,0:37:42.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,四百九\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1,600!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.08,0:38:24.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮我甩掉这些混蛋  默里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get those bastards off me, Murray!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.98,0:39:31.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们离开这里  默里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's get out of here, Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.25,0:39:42.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们摧毁了大部分轰炸机  但还剩一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We got most of the bombers, but not all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.89,0:39:44.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,看起来他们差点把你打下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looks like they almost got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.46,0:39:46.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  但弹药不够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, not enough lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.58,0:39:51.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么  刺激过头了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What, too much excitement for ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.80,0:39:53.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想赢得勋章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not looking to win a medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.83,0:39:53.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(380,235)\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}意指战死
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.22,0:39:56.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗  海军会让你赔这架飞机的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, the Navy's gonna make you pay for this aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.18,0:39:58.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们情况怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How'd you boys do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.58,0:40:00.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,霍平阵亡了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We lost Hopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.16,0:40:03.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,他俯冲后没能拉起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He never pulled out of his dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.38,0:40:06.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,情况不妙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.26,0:40:14.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,双引擎轰炸机  五点钟方向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Twin-engine bombers, five o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.05,0:40:28.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些该死的炮手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Goddamn gunners.
