Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.78,1:06:12.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知没有  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not that I know of, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.84,1:06:15.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,但那证明了中途岛就是AF\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that proves Midway is AF.
