Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.29,1:06:52.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,麦克  我想我们找到拍摄地点了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mack, I think we found the spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.08,1:06:53.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,说不好  福特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't say, Mr. Ford,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.11,1:06:55.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我曾帮好莱坞一位当红导演\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I've ever helped a big-time Hollywood director
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.13,1:06:56.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,做过采景\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}scout for a movie before.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.95,1:06:58.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,你打算在这么个鸟不拉屎的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What kind of film you planning to make
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.28,1:07:00.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,拍什么样的电影啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in a godforsaken place like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.57,1:07:02.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在海军的朋友说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Friend of mine in the Navy said
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.25,1:07:04.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也许能在这里找到真正的场面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I might be able to find some real action here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.43,1:07:07.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我被骗了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I've been hoodwinked.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.50,1:07:08.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说不好  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.53,1:07:10.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,从我们在这座小岛上设防的情况来看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From the way we've been fortifying this little island,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.30,1:07:12.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友的情报还真靠谱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd say your friend has some good intel.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.37,1:07:17.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,立正致意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Attention on deck.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.35,1:07:20.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,真好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.14,1:07:22.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,快给我坐下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sit the hell down.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.64,1:07:26.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,长话短说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna keep this short.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.54,1:07:28.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们中有些人认为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know some of you thought
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.34,1:07:30.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是个难应付的二把手  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was a pain in the ass as XO but...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.57,1:07:33.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是更难应付的还在后面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, that's about to get worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.43,1:07:35.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要回到珍珠港补给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're headed back to Pearl to resupply,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.00,1:07:36.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,这可能意味着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and it's probably because something big
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.73,1:07:38.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,有大事要发生了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is coming down the pipe.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.94,1:07:40.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,因此我们的侦察频率得加倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm therefore doubling our scouting flights
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.80,1:07:42.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你们一有机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I expect you to practice diving runs
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.77,1:07:44.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,就练习俯冲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}whenever you get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.74,1:07:45.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,面对日军时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't be the man
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.42,1:07:48.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,别做那个拖中队后腿的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who lets down the squadron when we finally face the Japs.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.33,1:07:51.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,解散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.80,1:08:00.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能跟您谈谈吗  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I talk to you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.71,1:08:06.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我能否做到  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know if I can do this, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.03,1:08:08.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我曾认为自己是个优秀的飞行员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought I was a good pilot,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.24,1:08:11.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我对自己失去了信心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I've lost my confidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.17,1:08:16.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要当飞行员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why did you become a pilot?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.95,1:08:20.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲希望你成为军官  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your dad wanted you to be an officer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.11,1:08:25.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,其实我父亲不怎么尊重军官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Actually, my dad didn't have much respect for officers.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.33,1:08:28.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说大多数军官都是蠢货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Said that most of them didn't know their ass from their elbow.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.72,1:08:32.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲是个顽固的混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, my dad was a tough son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.94,1:08:34.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我是怎么得到他的尊重的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know how I got his respect?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.32,1:08:37.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一直坚守战场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By always staying in the fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.43,1:08:39.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也希望有闲暇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish I had the luxury
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.44,1:08:40.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,顾及你的自信心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of worrying about your confidence,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.94,1:08:42.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们正缺飞行员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we're short on pilots,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.61,1:08:45.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以你得咬咬牙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so, you gotta suck it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.18,1:08:47.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,是  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.25,1:08:50.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.50,1:08:56.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,从现在起  你就是我的僚机了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From now on, you're my wingman.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.28,1:08:58.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会照应你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll be lookin' out for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.13,1:09:01.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,去换好衣服  准备侦察吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now go suit up for a scouting flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.37,1:09:05.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.47,1:09:07.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的秘诀是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's your secret?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.44,1:09:09.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的秘诀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My secret?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.63,1:09:11.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,他想知道你为什么无忧无虑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He wants to know why nothing bothers you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.18,1:09:15.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我叔叔曾是帝国大厦的一名焊工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My uncle was a welder on the Empire State Building.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.45,1:09:17.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,他在三百米高空上的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'd walk on a beam,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.72,1:09:20.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,钢梁上走动  不系安全绳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1,000 feet up in the sky, no ropes, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.20,1:09:21.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家都觉得他疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And everyone thought he was crazy,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.21,1:09:23.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,但于他而言  他只是在做分内之事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but to him, he was just doing a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.17,1:09:25.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,后来的一个周日  他从教堂回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And one Sunday, he's walking home from church.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.98,1:09:27.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,在离家只有一个街区时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's a block away from his house,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.32,1:09:29.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,一辆的士冲上了人行道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when a cab jumps over the curb,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.42,1:09:31.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,像碾死一只虫子那样撞死了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}splatters him like a bug.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.14,1:09:33.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你无从知晓自己的结局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You never know what's gonna get you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.20,1:09:35.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以何必为之烦忧呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, why worry about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.28,1:09:40.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,出发吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.10,1:09:43.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,这只是简单的侦察任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Simple scouting mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.87,1:09:46.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,回来的路上  我们练习俯冲  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On the way home, we'll practice the dive, you got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.35,1:09:47.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,是  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.06,1:09:48.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,这次我们的幅度会更大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll be going deeper this time,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.63,1:09:50.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以在最低点时别太快拉起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so don't pull up too fast on the bottom
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.64,1:09:51.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,否则你会晕过去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or you'll black out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.71,1:10:12.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.03,1:10:15.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,航母的航速太慢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship's moving too slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.16,1:10:44.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,中止  中止起飞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Abort! Abort takeoff!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.80,1:10:48.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,航速太慢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship's too slow!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.51,1:10:51.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,无法产生起飞所需的风速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not generating enough wind for launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.85,1:10:53.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  停下  停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.44,1:11:09.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,飞机落水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Plane in water.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.65,1:11:10.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,飞机落水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Plane in water.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.82,1:11:12.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,右转舵  该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Turn starboard, God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.65,1:11:14.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,右转舵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Turn starboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.11,1:11:36.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\b1\bord0\shad1\fad(1500,0)\c&H06126F&\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\pos(19.2,184)}1942年5月29日
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.57,1:11:36.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\b1\bord0\shad1\fad(1500,0)\c&H06126F&\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\pos(21,234.4)}珍珠港
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.04,1:11:54.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你也不喜欢系上领口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guess you don't like the chokers either.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.70,1:11:58.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我光是扣上扣子就弄得油腻腻了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd get grease on that thing just trying to button it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.39,1:12:00.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我看起来像个服务生一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Makes me look like a damn waiter.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.05,1:12:04.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,没人会把你错认成服务生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nobody would ever confuse you for a waiter.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.90,1:12:08.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很糟糕  比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You look like hell, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.67,1:12:09.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.72,1:12:12.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,疲倦而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.74,1:12:14.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,舰上的每个人都很疲倦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every man on the ship's tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.70,1:12:16.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经连轴转六个月了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've been out six months without a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.59,1:12:17.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在的鬼样子和疲倦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a big difference
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.56,1:12:20.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是有很大区别的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}between tired and whatever the hell you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.86,1:12:23.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,你得去陆地上的医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're going ashore to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.64,1:12:25.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这像是战伤吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does this look like a battle wound to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.84,1:12:27.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,只是皮疹而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a damn rash.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.49,1:12:29.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们的司令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, what are my men gonna think
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.51,1:12:31.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,决定跑去休假\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when their admiral up and decides
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.20,1:12:32.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的部下会怎么想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he needs a vacation?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.76,1:12:34.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令  比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a direct order, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.70,1:12:45.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不断损兵折将\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we keep losing men.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.30,1:12:47.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,甚至还没和日军交火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not even the Japs.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.14,1:12:49.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,赫尔曼在起飞时坠机了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Herman crashed on takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.77,1:12:51.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆·杜尔金在巡逻时失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tom Durkin disappeared on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.20,1:12:53.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有那个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And there's this other kid...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.33,1:12:56.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,威利·韦斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Willie West.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.58,1:12:58.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,他在出发前就觉得自己做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He didn't think he could cut it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.55,1:13:01.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,我以为那只是正常的紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I figured it was just the usual jitters.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.26,1:13:03.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想要保护他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I take him under my wing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.72,1:13:08.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,昨天我给他母亲写了封信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wrote a letter to his mother yesterday
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.91,1:13:10.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉她我没能保护好他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}telling her I failed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.90,1:13:21.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.39,1:13:23.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,他应该感到害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was right to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.62,1:13:27.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道大战降临\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everybody knows something big is coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.31,1:13:29.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要用几十架飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're talking about a couple dozen planes
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.70,1:13:31.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,对抗日军的整支舰队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}against the whole Japanese fleet.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.96,1:13:34.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们输了  他们就会称霸太平洋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if we lose, they own the Pacific,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.86,1:13:36.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,随后袭击西海岸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they raid the West Coast.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.64,1:13:40.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,西雅图  旧金山  洛杉矶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seattle, San Francisco, Los Angeles...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.72,1:13:42.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,都将陷入战火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will burn.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.16,1:13:45.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且这次战争将持续十年之久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And this damn war will last a decade.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.97,1:13:50.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从未见过你如此担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never seen you this worried before.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.30,1:13:53.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果只是我和我的飞机  我从不担忧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never had to worry when it was just me and my plane...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.44,1:13:58.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是这次不一样  安  我得领导这些士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but, Ann, it's different now. I have to lead these men.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.68,1:14:01.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我该跟他们说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do I say to them?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.62,1:14:03.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.59,1:14:05.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,坦诚就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}be honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.19,1:14:09.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,让他们看见我所看见的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And let them see what I can see.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.02,1:14:14.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们就会追随你到天涯海角  迪克·贝斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll follow you anywhere, Dick Best.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.83,1:14:35.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\b1\bord0\shad1\fad(1500,500)\c&H06126F&\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\pos(21,188)}美国海军约克城号
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.46,1:14:35.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\b1\bord0\shad1\fad(1500,1500)\c&H06126F&\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\pos(19.8,237.6)}珍珠港  干船坞
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.56,1:14:37.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,长官  约克城号被一枚230公斤的炸弹击中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, the Yorktown was hit by a 500-pound bomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.92,1:14:39.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要至少两周时间来修复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need at least two weeks for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.88,1:14:40.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.58,1:14:44.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们初步预测要在西雅图的干船坞停靠三个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our initial estimate was three months in dry dock in Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.60,1:14:51.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要这艘航母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need this ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.72,1:14:55.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不管你用什么材料修补甲板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't care if you need to patch the deck with plywood.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.09,1:14:58.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,约克城号72小时后必须起航\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yorktown sails in 72 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.36,1:15:02.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔西暂时离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Halsey is out.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.08,1:15:04.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,他由于皮疹住进了医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's in the hospital with shingles.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.76,1:15:07.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,因此我将第十六特混舰队的指挥权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I've given command of Task Force 16
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.40,1:15:08.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,交给斯普鲁恩斯少将\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to Admiral Spruance.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.93,1:15:10.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要设置陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're setting a trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.32,1:15:11.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的航母将在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our carriers will lie in wait
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.60,1:15:13.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,中途岛的东北方向待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}northeast of Midway.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.30,1:15:17.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里设下了一条潜艇警戒线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, we have set up a picket line of submarines here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.47,1:15:18.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,至于中途岛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As for Midway itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.68,1:15:22.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经在跑道上塞满了所有能抽出的飞机了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we have crammed every plane we can spare onto that runway.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.15,1:15:24.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过这一次  如果我们运气好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But this time, if we're lucky,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.40,1:15:26.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们将打日军一个措手不及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}surprise will be on our side.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.79,1:15:31.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱顿  关于日军方位的估算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Layton, how reliable are these estimates
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.18,1:15:32.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,有多准确\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the Japanese positions?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.85,1:15:34.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们根据现有情报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They represent our best guess,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.46,1:15:36.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,做出的最佳推测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}based on the intelligence that we have.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.38,1:15:38.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不能根据你的推测来制定作战计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't plan around your guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.77,1:15:42.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们的要求有些苛刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I understand that we're asking the impossible,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.89,1:15:45.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你得具体一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we need you to be specific.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.46,1:15:49.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,日军将于6月4日清晨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Japanese will attack on the morning of June 4th
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.94,1:15:53.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,从西北方向来袭  方位325度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from the northwest, at a bearing of 325 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.04,1:15:56.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,在离中途岛280公里处被我们发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They will be sighted 175 miles from Midway
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.80,1:15:59.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,时间为当地时间7点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at 0700 local time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.48,1:16:03.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我相信莱顿及其团队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I trust Layton and his team.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.44,1:16:06.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,制定相应的作战计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make your plans accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.08,1:16:07.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,解散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dismissed.
