Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.98,1:18:07.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,它是怎么及时开出干船坞的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How the hell did she get out of dry dock in time?
