Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.03,1:18:12.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想每场战役都需要奇迹吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I guess every battle needs a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.95,1:18:18.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个沙盘上的每个位置你都记得一清二楚  莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've memorized every position on that board, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.75,1:18:19.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.96,1:18:22.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我打算在这里过夜  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I'm going to spend the night here, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.13,1:18:23.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,以防出现什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just in case anything comes up.
