Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.51,1:18:27.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,她知道我们这一行是怎样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, she knows the drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.38,1:18:30.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子也知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My wife knows the drill, too,
