Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.21,1:19:07.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们起飞了全部飞行中队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They've scrambled all the squadrons.
