Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.67,1:19:12.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好  麦奇  这样很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's great, Mikey, that's great.
