Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.93,1:19:16.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,-好的  先生  -高一点  很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- All right, sir. - A little higher. Good.
