Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.95,1:19:38.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家都觉得我们没法跟日军较量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nobody thinks we can go toe-to-toe with the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.50,1:19:40.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,觉得正常情况我们打不过他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not in a fair fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.42,1:19:44.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天  我们完全不被看好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Today, we're gonna be big underdogs.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.21,1:19:46.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Me?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.17,1:19:48.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这个房间里的人敢在天上跟任何人斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think the men in this room can fly with anyone.
