Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.34,1:19:55.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,但也因为我见识过你们的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it's also because I've seen what you can do.
