Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.73,1:20:10.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要把他们打得屁滚尿流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're gonna give 'em a shellackin'.
