Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.82,1:20:52.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了  日军来袭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're coming! The Japs are coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.15,1:20:54.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,福特先生  敌机来袭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Ford, we have incoming aircrafts.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.40,1:20:55.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得让你进入掩体了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to get you to a bunker.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.32,1:20:59.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,敌机来袭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Incoming aircrafts?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.41,1:21:01.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生  你必须要进掩体了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, you have to take cover, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.08,1:21:05.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,该死  快上屋顶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Holy shit! To the roof!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.37,1:21:06.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,福特先生  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Ford, wait!
