Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.79,1:21:10.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你不进入掩体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there isn't going to be a movie, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.09,1:21:12.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,-就没法活下来拍电影了  -我可得把这个拍下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- if we don't get you to cover. - I'm gonna shoot the damn picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.17,1:21:14.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了吗  杰基\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Got it, Jackie?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.93,1:21:16.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.99,1:21:35.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.82,1:21:38.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,继续拍摄  继续拍摄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keep shooting. Keep shooting!
