Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.30,1:21:56.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱顿  你跟罗彻福特只算差了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, Layton, you and Rochefort were only off
