Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.04,1:45:45.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,有烟吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.46,1:46:03.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  我在珍珠港有很多朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, I had a lot of friends at Pearl Harbor.
