Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.86,1:47:36.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道要跟着那艘日本驱逐舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, how'd you know to follow that Jap destroyer?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.97,1:47:38.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,凭直觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I played a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.70,1:47:40.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的直觉可能帮助我们赢得了这场战役\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, your hunch might have won us this battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.37,1:47:42.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我不得不说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I gotta tell ya,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.49,1:47:46.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看那很像牛仔脾气那一套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that looked like some cowboy bullshit to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.03,1:47:49.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不能打败他们  那就加入他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if you can't beat 'em, join 'em.
