Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.33,1:47:58.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,飞行员正要上来报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The pilots are coming up to report.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.80,1:48:02.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,敌军舰队有什么新动向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the news from the enemy fleet?
