Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.46,1:48:10.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,俯冲轰炸机呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about the dive bombers?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.18,1:48:12.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们也许还能集结十几架\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can probably scrounge up a dozen.
