Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.46,1:48:26.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,是  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.37,1:48:32.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,您没事吧  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You okay, sir?
