Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.70,1:48:51.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,有没有迪金森的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Has anybody heard from Dickinson?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.41,1:48:53.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.82,1:48:54.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,暂时还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.47,1:48:58.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们刚从鬼门关走了一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I know you boys have just been through hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.30,1:49:01.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们得回去  击毁敌军的最后一艘航母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we gotta go back and hit the last carrier.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.68,1:49:15.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看看能不能找到更多的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll see if I can find more men.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.61,1:49:36.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,穿衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Strap up.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.93,1:49:39.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要出发了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're going back out.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.10,1:49:42.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  长官  您还是找别人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, sir, but I think you need to find somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.62,1:49:46.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,您不知道坐在后座上是什么感觉  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't know what it's like to be in the back seat, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.45,1:49:48.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,就好像您根本不在乎我们能不能活着回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You fly like you don't care if we come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.40,1:50:01.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也想回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanna go home, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.55,1:50:05.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想每次回家都只能跟妻子待那么几天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanna spend more than a few days at a time with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.39,1:50:08.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,也想看着我的女儿长大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See my little girl grow up.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.01,1:50:10.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you're right.
