Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.26,1:50:22.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,等待驰援\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}till the cavalry arrives.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.00,1:50:28.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真的不能飞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, if you really can't fly,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.79,1:50:30.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会去找别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.72,1:50:32.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你应该坐回那架飞机上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you should get back in that plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.76,1:50:36.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的余生都会记得这一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll remember this moment for the rest of your life.
