Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.66,1:50:40.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你挺过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when people were counting on you,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.72,1:50:42.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,以后不管遇到什么  你都有能力面对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you'll be able to face anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.95,1:50:56.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经经历了那么多  默里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've come this far, Murray.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.00,1:51:00.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,别让我独自回到战场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't make me go back out there without you.
